---
import SubpageLayout from '../../../layouts/SubpageLayout.astro';
---

<SubpageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Custom AI"
  subtitle="Custom AI applications, built with your team. From prototype to production."
  seoDescription="Custom AI solutions by AI Heroes. Custom AI applications, integration into existing systems, from prototype to production. Built with your team."
  accentColor="blue"
  pillarBadge="Software & Implementation"
  ctaLabel="Discuss your project"
  trustedBy={["OLX Poland", "iFood Brazil", "Trabu", "TicketGenie"]}
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">From idea to working AI solution</h2>

    <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      You know what you want to build, or you have a roadmap that makes clear which AI solution delivers the most value. Now you need a team that can build it. We provide the expertise, independently or alongside your developers.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-brand-blue not-prose">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-3">What we build</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 list-disc ml-5">
        <li>Custom AI applications tailored to your use case</li>
        <li>Integration of AI into existing systems and workflows</li>
        <li>RAG pipelines for internal knowledge bases</li>
        <li>AI assistants and chatbots with your business context</li>
        <li>Automation of repetitive processes with AI</li>
        <li>Proof of concepts and prototypes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">How we work</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-4xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-3">1</div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Scoping</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Together we define what needs to be built, with which technology, and how it fits your existing landscape.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-4xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-3">2</div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Build</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Agile development in short sprints. Regular demos so you always see where we stand.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-4xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-3">3</div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Delivery</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Working software, documentation and training of your team to work with it.</p></div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">Examples</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <a href="/en/cases/medux" class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200 hover:border-brand-blue transition-colors group"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors mb-2">Medux</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Reduced AI costs by 70% through custom optimisation of their AI workflow.</p></a>
      <a href="/en/cases/trabu" class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200 hover:border-brand-blue transition-colors group"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark group-hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors mb-2">Trabu</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Custom AI integration that automated translation processes and improved quality.</p></a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-2">From €15,000</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Per project</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-2">2-12 weeks</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Timeline</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-blue mb-2">Your team</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Involved</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="dark-box-content bg-brand-dark p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-red my-8 not-prose">
      <h3>The full journey under one roof</h3>
      <p>We build, and we <a href="/en/services/ai-foundations" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">train your team</a> to work with the solution. With our <a href="/en/services/opportunity-scouting" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">consulting</a> you know for sure you're building the right thing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SubpageLayout>
